{"tid":1025742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國 西班牙出招打擊華人洗黑錢","createTime":"2019-02-17T14:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T15:06:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eb19cf8480414c545cdcccaf192a19aecf4af310","tid":1025742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190217/20614369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F20614369&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=eb475ca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F20614369&h=41c346e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190217/20614369</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國 西班牙出招打擊華人洗黑錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190217/large/17cx103p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190217%2Flarge%2F17cx103p.jpg&h=1a12d127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國示威者不滿銀行戶口被凍結，在西班牙對外銀行外面抗議。路透社<br />\n<br />\n中國是世界第一大奢侈品消費國，除了親身飛到歐洲買名牌，也有不少買家透過「代購」選購心頭好。法國傳媒報道，中國有不法分子以代購為名，實則從事洗黑錢、走私及逃稅等違法行為。法國警方估計，這些「代購網絡」每年從中獲利高達500萬歐元(4,400萬港元)，全部沒繳稅，當地警方逮捕至少6名中國人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190217/large/17cx105p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190217%2Flarge%2F17cx105p.jpg&h=6908a8ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀行門外被示威者貼滿抗議貼紙。路透社<br />\n<br />\n西班牙華人被凍結戶口示威<br />\n<br />\n法國傳媒報道，警方去年8月份接獲線報，指有人專門在法國百貨公司購買名牌手袋，再到中國以高價出售牟利，他們僱用一些持觀光簽證來法的人，指示他們以護照影印本購物，並將退稅當作報酬，所獲金額有時甚至能賺取機票費用。警方監視多名中國人，隨後在疑犯住所中搜出大量名牌，包括LV、CHANEL、Gucci，並拘捕6名中國男女。法國警方估計，犯罪網絡透過代購方式漂白數億歐元。<br />\n<br />\n隨着代購規模越來越大，中國2019年實施《電子商務法》限制代購活動，規定個人或商戶接受監管及繳稅，違規可被罰款200萬人民幣(約231萬港元)。<br />\n<br />\n同時，西班牙有數百名華人上周五（15日）在馬德里示威，指不滿西班牙對外銀行（BBVA）以涉嫌洗錢為由，在沒有事先通知下凍結其銀行戶口，直斥「種族歧視」。BBVA解釋是為打擊洗黑錢活動。<br />\n<br />\n中央社<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n湖南甘肅12食品廠 爆非洲豬瘟病毒<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n特朗普唱好中美會談 或延休戰期"},{"pid":"3e6eee0518e8c27d39c4da33cd2fa01b70b67247","tid":1025742,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx%2Fi%2FsWkHesT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%252Fi%252FsWkHesT.gif&h=7e77add3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a52959960f6b341c54e8ea514b68f9392af0788","tid":1025742,"uid":126312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:33:42.000Z","msg":"仲唱埋國歌添.咁撚愛國死返支那啦成班生番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb89cfe84213c4301b83d7d2a16b73cfef1c6a39","tid":1025742,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"而家日本最親中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4896e59b5a0f027b86ab06b868c1e6b2bbe19a1c","tid":1025742,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03a6411f21e53f4f07c87a23e13cfa691b32847","tid":1025742,"uid":21052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:54:31.000Z","msg":"抵啦<br />\n癌細胞真係去到邊柒到邊"},{"pid":"82f8cfd993ed86d35b05d9e3f1128a17d09d0262","tid":1025742,"uid":74509,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"成班係到破壞社會安定繁榮，不思進取，我的國真係一代不如一代"},{"pid":"34c65ce7c44b18ea54d7a75e304e17ed60f73209","tid":1025742,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:58:44.000Z","msg":"支那畜有樣睇, 隻隻都陰陰濕濕"},{"pid":"d9a05f644820a81ca0c90cf61622df80a7d203cd","tid":1025742,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:05:12.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩d蝗，有襯乜事都要咁政府化，又要去人地國家但又唔守法"},{"pid":"54b86e2ae938a52730449361c07e7e3d94bc4a16","tid":1025742,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab76fe6374ea24eef26a0145224afc3fd729e90f","tid":1025742,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb89cfe84213c4301b83d7d2a16b73cfef1c6a39","tid":1025742,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"而家日本最親中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"仲有德國"}]}